<p align="center"><strong>THE FAULT IN OUR STARS HOME ENTERTAINMENT  SWEEPSTAKES</strong><br />
  <a name="_DV_M5" id="_DV_M5"></a><strong>OFFICIAL RULES</strong></p>
<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p><a name="_DV_M6" id="_DV_M6"></a><strong>NO  PURCHASE NECESSARY. MAKING A PURCHASE WILL NOT IMPROVE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING.<a name="_DV_M7" id="_DV_M7"></a></strong><br />
  <strong>PROMOTION  DESCRIPTION:</strong> <em>The Fault In Our Stars </em>Home Entertainment  Sweepstakes (the &ldquo;Promotion&rdquo;) begins on August 26, 2014 at 12:00:00 AM Eastern  Time (ET) and ends <a name="_DV_M8" id="_DV_M8"></a>September 30, 2014 at 11:59:59 PM ET  (the<strong> </strong>&quot;Promotion Period&quot;).  Each entrant (each, a &ldquo;Participant&rdquo;) unconditionally accepts and agrees to  comply with and abide by these Official Rules and the decisions of Twentieth  Century Fox Home Entertainment LLC (the &quot;Sponsor&quot;) which shall be  final and binding in all respects. <a name="_DV_M9" id="_DV_M9"></a><strong></strong><br />
  <strong>PROMOTION ELIGIBILITY:</strong> The Promotion  is open only to legal residents of the 50 United States, District Columbia  (U.S.), and Canada (excluding Quebec) age 21 or older at the time of entry, or  if a Canadian resident, who are above the age of majority in the province or  territory in which they reside at the time of entry. Void outside these  geographic areas and wherever else prohibited by law.  Employees, officers and directors of Sponsor, it&rsquo;s respective parents,  subsidiaries, affiliates, independent sales distributors, prize providers,  advertising and promotional agencies (collectively &ldquo;Sweepstakes Entities&rdquo;) (and  immediate family members or those living in the same household with such  individuals), are not eligible to participate.  All federal, state provincial and local laws and regulations apply.  <strong></strong><br />
  <a name="_DV_M10" id="_DV_M10"></a><strong>HOW TO ENTER: </strong>To enter the  Sweepstakes, visit <a href="http://www.mylittleinfinity.com">www.mylittleinfinity.com</a>  (the &ldquo;Website&rdquo;) during the Promotion  Period and follow all entry instructions to complete the entry process  (the &ldquo;Entry&rdquo;)<a name="_DV_M16" id="_DV_M16"></a>.  <strong>Limit: One (1)  Entry per person during the Promotion Period, </strong>regardless  of whether entrant has more than one email address<strong>.</strong>  All methods of entry have an equal chance of  winning. All entries become the property of the Sponsor and will not be  acknowledged or returned.  Online  entrants are subject to all notices posted online including but not limited to  the Sponsor&rsquo;s Privacy Policy.  </p>
<p><strong>PRIZE DETAILS  /APPROXIMATE </strong><strong>RETAIL VALUE</strong> (&ldquo;ARV&rdquo;): <a name="_DV_M18" id="_DV_M18"></a>There will be one (1) Grand Prize consisting of a trip  for one (1) (Grand Prize Winner and his/her guest), to Amsterdam.  The Amsterdam  Grand Prize trip includes the following:</p>
<ul type="disc">
  <li>Orange Tulip Delivery to       the winner&rsquo;s home address, to include prize details and itinerary.<u></u></li>
  <li>Round-trip coach airfare       for two (2) to Amsterdam, from a       US major airport. <u></u></li>
  <li>Roundtrip Airport       Transfers in Amsterdam, in a private luxury vehicle; <u></u></li>
  <li>Three (3) night hotel       accommodation at the Sandton Hotel De Filosoof.<u></u></li>
  <li>Entrance for two (2)       people to the historic landmark of Anne Frank&rsquo;s House.<u></u></li>
  <li>$150 to spend on the       perfect dress or outfit.<u></u></li>
  <li>VIP two (2) hour       candlelight cruise for tow (2), along Amsterdam&rsquo;s famous canals on a       glass-roofed boat, with soft drinks and snacks, and fantastic waterfront       views.<u></u></li>
  <li>Dinner for two (2) at       Restaurant De Kas: (ARV $250), including roundtrip restaurant transfers.<u></u></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>TOTAL ARV of Grand Prize: $4,975.00 </strong></p>
<p><strong>ODDS:</strong> Odds of  winning depend on the number of eligible entries received during the Promotion  Period.<a name="_DV_M25" id="_DV_M25"></a><br />
  <strong></strong><br />
  <strong>WINNER  SELECTION:</strong> Winner  will be selected in a random drawing on or about October 7, 2014, from among  all eligible entries received during the Promotion Period,  conducted by an independent judging agency and whose decisions are final. <br />
  <br />
  <strong>WINNER  NOTIFICATION:</strong>  <strong>Grand Prize winner will be  confirmed via email, mail and/or phone. </strong><br />
  <strong>US residents </strong>will  be required<strong> to  sign and return, within ten (10) days of notification, an Affidavit of  Eligibility, a Liability Waiver, a W-9 Form and where allowable, a Publicity  Release (collectively, &quot;the Releases&quot;). </strong>These releases  will require the Winner to furnish his/her Social Security Number for the sole  purpose of tax reporting, as required by law.  <br />
  <strong>Canadian residents</strong> will be  required <strong>within ten (10) days of  notification</strong>: (a) to <strong>sign and return, an Declaration a  Publicity Release </strong>and (b) to correctly answer a time-limited  mathematical skill-testing question via return mail or email without assistance  or mechanical aid <strong>(collectively, &quot;the  Releases&quot;)</strong>.  <br />
  <br />
  Failure to return the documents and/or information requested by a winner, or  the return of any prize or prize notification as undeliverable, or if a Winner  is found to be ineligible or otherwise not in compliance with these Official  Rules, the prize will be forfeited and an alternate potential winner may be  selected in a random drawing from among all remaining eligible entries.  Travel companion of winner will also be  required to sign a travel liability waiver. Noncompliance  will result in disqualification and an alternate winner may be selected.<strong>  </strong><strong><u>The prize will be awarded within  approximately 45 days after the winner is verified.<br />
  </u></strong><strong><br />
</strong><strong>PRIZE CONDITIONS:</strong>  All travel-related expenses included but not  limited to ground transportation to and from home to the major US airport,  taxes, gratuities, incidentals, upgrades, insurance, service charges, airport  surcharges<em>,</em> departure taxes, hotel,  resort or property fees, food &amp; beverage and personal expenses such as  telephone/Internet charges, and gift shop purchases are the sole responsibility  of prize winner and guest.  Accommodation  is based on two (2) guests sharing one (1) hotel room and a valid credit or  debit card will be required to guarantee any incidentals on check in.  All elements of the prize are subject to  availability; once confirmed, the prize cannot be amended or cancelled.  <strong>Winner and guest must have valid photo ID and  passport prior to departure</strong> and passport must be  valid for at least 6 months as of the date of travel, any necessary visas or  insurance are the responsibility of the winner and guests.  Prize cannot be taken over Christmas, New  Year, Thanksgiving or on US or Dutch public holidays and stay must include a  Saturday night.  Prize is valid for twelve  (12) months from date of notification of winning and all travel must be completed  within that time. Exact color of tulips may vary. Winner and guest must travel on same itinerary. </p>
<p>All hotel reservations are based on availability  and all holidays are excluded. Accommodations are subject to availability at  time of reservation. Blackout dates, advance booking requirements and travel  restrictions may apply. Availability is subject to factors such as weather,  seasonality and space availability. Reservations are subject to availability.  If weather affects the ability for winner and his/her guest to redeem any  portion of prize during the scheduled date and time, then the Sponsor shall  have no further obligation to the winner and/or guest other than to supply the  remaining elements of the prize package minus the unused portion of prize. If  for any reason whatsoever, winner and/or guest are unable to travel after all  travel arrangements have been made and paid, the Sponsor shall have no further  obligation to the winner. If Grand Prize is forfeited prior to Sponsor  finalizing and paying for travel, and there is sufficient time to notify an  alternate winner, the prize will be awarded to an alternate winner in a  separate random drawing from among all non-winning eligible entries. Winner and  guest are responsible for obtaining the proper travel documentation (e.g.,  valid photo ID) prior to travel. Winner&rsquo;s guest must be legal U.S. resident, 21 years or older and  must complete and return a Liability/Publicity/Travel Release prior to travel  as noted above. </p>
<p>If  a prize notification or prize is returned as undeliverable, or if winner is  found to be ineligible or not in compliance with these rules that winner will  be disqualified, and the prize may be awarded to an alternate winner in a  separate random drawing. </p>
<p>Prizes are not redeemable for cash. Prizes are  non-assignable or transferable. No substitution is permitted except if prize is  unavailable, in which case a prize of equal or greater value will be awarded.  No cash in lieu of prizes and no exchange or substitution of prizes, except at  the sole discretion of the Sponsor.Any other  incidental expenses on prize not specified herein are the winner&rsquo;s sole  responsibility.</p>
<p>Except  where prohibited by law, entry and acceptance of prize constitute permission to  use winner's name, prize won, hometown, likeness, video tape, photographs, and  statements for purposes of advertising, promotion and publicity (including  online posting) in any and all media now or hereafter known throughout the  world in perpetuity, without additional compensation, notification or  permission.<br />
