<p><a name="_DV_M30" id="_DV_M30"></a><strong>TECHNOLOGY  CONDITIONS</strong>:  The Sweepstakes Entities assume no responsibility for any damage to a  Participant's computer, mobile device or telephone system that is directly or  indirectly caused by accessing the Website or otherwise participating in the  Promotion, or for any computer system, mobile device operating or other system,  phone line, hardware, software or program malfunctions, or other errors,  failures, dropped or delayed computer or wireless transmissions or network  connections that are human or technical in nature. The Website's database clock  will be the official timekeeper for this Promotion. Once submitted, subject to  the Website&rsquo;s terms of use, entries become the property of the Sponsor. Except  as otherwise provided in these Official Rules, information collected in  connection with the Promotion will be used by Sponsor in accordance with Fox&rsquo;s  online privacy policy, located at http://www.foxconnect.com/privacy_policy.  Entry in the Promotion must be made by the  Participant and only at the Website or App Site. </p>
