<p><strong>WINNERS LIST: </strong>To receive an  Official Winner&rsquo;s List for the Promotion, send a self-addressed stamped  envelope to: <em>The Fault In Our Stars </em>Home  Entertainment Sweepstakes Winner&rsquo;s List Request, PO Box 16350, Rochester, NY  14616. The Winners List request must be received by November 4, 2014, and it will  be fulfilled following the awarding of the prizes.</p>
